      "continueOnFail": true,
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput",
      "notes": "VERIFY before activating: query param casing for /opportunities/search is unconfirmed in this session (legacy GHL endpoints sometimes use snake_case instead of the camelCase used elsewhere in v2). Check the real GHL docs / a test call and adjust location_id/pipeline_id/contact_id below if they don't match.",
